data.description: Could this be the one ? Brand new interior paint has been done !!!  Watch the sunsets each day from this awesome 4 bed home on over 2 acres  with POOL, Storm shelter and outbuildings, (horses ? Pigs? goats ? chickens ?) BRAND new roof, Pool is sparkling clear for those hot summer days,  septic, close to city yet the feel of country living an just a short drive to OKC, Yukon/Mustang. Dont delay - this home might need minor cosmetic updating but that's the FUN part ! Pre-approval letter with offers please, seller in process of painting interior !!  legal is 31-10N-05W BEG NW/C LOT 4 ON W LINE OF LOT 4, TH E 481.3', TH S 224', TH W 481.3', TH N 224' TO POB. buyer to verify schools
